data.title: Bjorn Andreas Bull
data.meta_description: Bjorn Andreas Bull-Hansen. Writer: Iskaldt. Bjorn Andreas Bull-Hansen was born in Oslo, Norway in 1972 and had his first novel published at the young age of 24. He has written several novels and has become known as a modern day Viking, both because of his novels and also because of his lifestyle and life philosophy. He is a bilingual writer and works both in the US and Norway.
